title: Artyushinskaya
text:
Artyushinskaya () is a <a href="types%20of%20inhabited%20localities%20in%20Russia">rural locality</a> (a <a href="Village%23Russia">village</a>) in Osinovskoye Rural Settlement of <a href="Vinogradovsky%20District">Vinogradovsky District</a>, <a href="Arkhangelsk%20Oblast">Arkhangelsk Oblast</a>, Russia. The population was 25 as of 2010.
Geography.
Artyushinskaya is located 33 km southeast of <a href="Bereznik%2C_Vinogradovsky_District%2C_Arkhangelsk_Oblast">Bereznik</a> (the district's administrative centre) by road. Morshikhinskaya is the nearest rural locality.
